name: PERFUME FAM OUD 60ml
campo_tres: An intense vibration of flamboyant red spices combine in perfect harmony with the warm woodland tones, in an embrace of powdery floral notes. Featuring saffron, chili, fresh rose, oud, cashmeran, rose powder, rubber sap, vinyl accord, sandalwood, cedar, milk and red musk.

This fragrance with its original scent transmits all the richness of oriental perfumes. Enclosed by hints of various woods and succulent citrus, this balanced line gives the perfume a fragrance which evokes wisdom and spirituality. The notes include bergamot, mandarin, star anise, rosewood, osmanthus, licorice, ginger, patchouli, tolu balsam, tobacco and vetiver.
